# Changelog

## 0.7.1 - 2025-07-18

- Replace `modname:` with regular expression in simplelootbags loot tables
- Updated simplelootbags loot tables to unstuck mid-game (early brass age) stall
- Add infection resistance to other, non-vanilla armors
- Added visual and particle effects for better ambiance

## 0.7.0 - 2025-07-13

- Initial version (submitted to modrinth moderators).
- Suitable for playtesting by friends
